&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Use Case&lt;/strong&gt;: AI tools like HubSpot or Mailchimp can automate email marketing campaigns, segmenting audiences and sending personalized messages based on user behavior.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pros&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
