&lt;h3 id="2-data-management"&gt;2. Data Management&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;AI tools can help manage and analyze data more effectively. They can automate data collection, cleaning, and analysis, allowing teams to make data-driven decisions faster.&lt;/p&gt;
